In this notebook, we are interested to figure out couple of insights in Data Talks Club slack channel.

  1. [x] WordCloud (most talked topics within the project course-data-engineering)
  2. [x] Network Graph, the people connected to each other (through, message replies, reactions, etc)
  3. Message frequency over time.
  4. [ ] Is there any correllation between people from similar time zones react with each other more or not.
